        "ggDh5WBLTXX_childItem_0": "<p>What is GemGut?</p>",
        "ggDh5WBLTXX_childItem_1": "<p>How is GemGut different from other probiotics?</p>",
        "ggDh5WBLTXX_childItem_2": "<p>How do I take GemGut?</p>",
        "ggDh5WBLTXX_childItem_3": "<p>When will I feel results?</p>",
        "ggDh5WBLTXX_childItem_4": "<p>Is GemGut safe for daily use?</p>",
        "ggDh5WBLTXX_childItem_5": "<p>Can I take GemGut with other supplements?</p>",
        "ggF5m6RVf9S_text": "<p>Need more answers about all our products?</p>",
        "ggHCtHoENbt_label": "<p><u>Check all product FAQs</u></p>",
        "ggHOwcuAQPj_label": "<p><u>Contact us</u></p>",
        "ggOyMKFjm98_text": "<p>Yes. GemGut is non-habit forming and designed to be part of your daily routine.</p>",
        "ggPUDAeFVJ0_label": "<p><u>Help Center</u></p>",
        "ggQkPMsKhug_text": "<p>Take 1–2 servings daily, preferably after meals. No preparation needed — designed for convenience.</p>",
        "ggRYmNyB4WA_text": "<p>Any purchase or account related information you can find in support articles.</p>",
        "ggYBCEATL9r_text": "<p>Most probiotics only focus on adding good bacteria. GemGut goes further by combining probiotics, digestive enzymes, and soothing extracts to support both immediate relief and long-term gut health.</p>",
        "ggblxfIWCkG_text": "Frequently Asked Questions",
        "ggddwOdB0vr_text": "<p>GemGut is a daily gut health supplement designed to support digestion, reduce bloating, and improve gut balance — especially for people dealing with stress-related digestive issues.</p>",
        "gghz5avlBXR_text": "<p>Many users notice reduced bloating and discomfort within 30–60 minutes, with more stable digestion over consistent use.</p>",
        "ggvte_AfM4S_text": "<p>Or drop us an email.</p>",
        "ggyaibY_PGH_text": "<p>In most cases, yes. However, if you’re on medication or have specific conditions, consult your healthcare provider. For best results, consistent daily use helps maintain a balanced gut microbiome and prevent recurring issues.</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-614247644859990683"
    },
