    "gp_section_614247644860056219": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "7201403e1e1a47bec852427688377d5f4589748de72e5ec1f4369eb9bb208868_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg4kmeLNBq__text": "<p>An imbalanced gut often means harmful bacteria have started to dominate. Instead of harsh elimination, GemGut uses natural prebiotic fibers to gently shift the ecosystem.</p><p>These fibers act as nourishment for beneficial bacteria while making it harder for harmful microbes to thrive. Over time, this helps rebalance your gut in a sustainable, non-aggressive way—without disrupting your body’s natural rhythm.</p>",
        "gg9bWe5bOeM_text": "<p>5</p>",
        "gg9h9cq3q1g_text": "Your digestion starts working efficiently again",
        "ggAtHTrsFA4_text": "<p>3</p>",
        "ggCxvUi54ZD_text": "Your gut stays balanced and resilient",
        "ggGeFm9cPeB_text": "<p>GemGut is a natural, multi-action formula designed to support your digestive system in real-life conditions—stress, irregular eating, and modern lifestyles. Instead of forcing quick fixes, it works with your body to gently reset, rebalance, and strengthen your gut over time.</p>",
        "ggH2SGXH890_text": "<p>2</p>",
        "ggPf9_rEacR_text": "<p>4</p>",
        "ggTlLhKKhqu_text": "<p>With the gut environment improved, live probiotic cultures (Lactobacillus &amp; Bifidobacterium) are able to settle and begin restoring a healthy microbiome.</p>",
        "gg_lJn1LmEG_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0946/3011/7697/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_78u0ju78u0ju78u0_1.png",
        "ggfTpx5ZIgt_text": "We reintroduce beneficial bacteria",
        "gggWglH-5hF_text": "<p>With consistent use, your gut becomes more stable, better at handling stress, and more efficient at absorbing nutrients—helping you feel lighter, more energized, and in control every day.</p>",
        "ggia2w4j2gV_text": "Here’s how it works",
        "ggo9OHOFVTa_text": "<p>Your gut is constantly affected by daily stress, кофе, fast food, and irregular eating habits. These factors can irritate your digestive system, leading to bloating, discomfort, and sluggish digestion.</p><p>GemGut begins with soothing botanical extracts like ginger, chamomile, and aloe vera to calm inflammation and relax the digestive tract. This creates a more stable internal environment—an essential first step before any real gut repair can happen.</p>",
        "ggqctov_oeF_text": "<p>Plant-based enzymes and peppermint support faster breakdown of food, reducing bloating, heaviness, and post-meal discomfort—often within 30–60 minutes.</p>",
        "ggrCvJZmH10_text": "We start by calming gut disruption",
        "ggrjkLuav32_text": "Then we reduce harmful bacteria",
        "ggwZMeOznWt_text": "<p>1</p>"
      },
