        "gg9EnXxua40_text": "<p>“I started taking GemGut mainly for bloating, and honestly I didn’t expect much at first because I’ve tried similar products before with little to no results. But within a couple of weeks, I noticed my stomach felt noticeably lighter after meals and I wasn’t getting that uncomfortable fullness as often. What surprised me most was how consistent it felt, not just a one-off good day but something that actually carried through. It made eating feel a lot less stressful and more normal again.”</p>",
        "ggC7-gJdHn2_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0946/3011/7697/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_78u0ju78u0ju78u0_2.png",
        "ggJx6PfAAHk_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggPIQTVHShh_text": "<p>4.7/5 based on 5,000+ customers</p>",
        "ggQ-zTzsLqH_text": "<p>Sophie L</p>",
        "ggWdwLtjwFM_text": "<p>“I’ve struggled with bloating for years, especially after meals, and it always made me feel uncomfortable and self-conscious in daily situations. Since using GemGut, the intensity has gone down significantly and my stomach feels much calmer overall after eating. It’s not about instant results, but the steady improvement is what made me keep using it consistently over time. I finally feel like my body is responding in a more balanced and predictable way.”</p>",
        "ggXvsT6xgHM_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0946/3011/7697/files/unnamed.png",
        "gga1HmzFmay_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0946/3011/7697/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_oi1849oi1849oi18.png",
        "ggg-LAkuVIO_text": "<p>“I didn’t think my digestion was that bad until I started noticing how much better I felt after using GemGut consistently over time. Less heaviness, less discomfort, and overall just a more ‘normal’ feeling after eating became more noticeable each week. What I like most is that it doesn’t feel like a quick fix, but something that actually supports my body. Now it’s part of my routine and something I don’t want to go without anymore.”</p>",
        "ggiWTYtL4CM_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggiufspNGGE_text": "<p>Sophie L</p>",
        "ggkPuaRw67N_text": "<p>“I came across GemGut after seeing it recommended a few times and was honestly pretty skeptical, especially since I’ve tried different probiotics before without much change. But after sticking with it for a few weeks, I started to notice my digestion felt more stable and less unpredictable throughout the day. I wasn’t constantly thinking about what I ate or how I’d feel after anymore, which made everything easier. It’s a small shift, but it made a real difference in my routine.”</p>",
        "ggnU4W40X5q_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0946/3011/7697/files/shutterstock_2608441401_1.jpg",
        "ggnVFPp1OQ9_text": "<p>Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggucvZ2V80B_text": "<p>Sophie L</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-614247645296198446"
    },
